{"tid":1709572,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美制裁5名委內瑞拉高官　涉侵犯人權及貪污","createTime":"2019-11-12T02:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T23:40:20.000Z","uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"697335e8b337ec566761d1e96779d5a372e3f51c","tid":1709572,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:20:03.000Z","msg":"美制裁5名委內瑞拉高官　涉侵犯人權及貪污<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20191107/bkn-20191107030013032-1107_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20191107%2Fbkn-20191107030013032-1107_00972_001.html&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=8aa6ae05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20191107/bkn-20191107030013032-1107_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國財政部周二（5日）宣布，制裁5名委內瑞拉高級官員。該5人均被指侵犯人權，暴力鎮壓反政府示威者及貪污。<br />\n<br />\n是次被制裁的高官均來自軍方或情報機關，他們分別是伊查索（Remigio Ceballos Ichaso）、烏爾塔多（Nestor Neptali Blanco Hurtado）、費雷拉（Jose Adelino Ornelas Ferreira）、埃斯科瓦爾（Pedro Miguel Carreno Escobar）及奇里諾斯（Carlos Alberto Calderon Chirinos）。他們早前已被加拿大及歐盟制裁。美方指，決定實施制裁是為了與加拿大及歐盟保持一致，一起制裁委內瑞拉總統馬杜羅政權的官員。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">根據美國規定，被美方制裁的人士，其在美國境內的資產將被凍結，美國公民亦不得與他們交易。委內瑞拉自今年年初以來陷入政治危機，反對派領袖瓜伊</span></span></strong>多自立為看守總統，獲美國、歐洲及拉丁美洲多國承認。"},{"pid":"0387df6a25ff12a0fe38b537e036f1e7cad4a8c3","tid":1709572,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T02:53:43.000Z","msg":"美國機構不能同佢交易先至傷，美金都無得用"},{"pid":"184ec0d27f92f1e4280f8f0abbed67eebda56c39","tid":1709572,"uid":178875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:00:17.000Z","msg":"一抄支那千萬黨員家<br />\n<br />\n美國財政儲備究竟可以多幾多兆美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能京都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0325fcc5a620dc18358bdfc1deaeacd9deb66756","tid":1709572,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"184ec0d27f92f1e4280f8f0abbed67eebda56c39","tid":1709572,"uid":178875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:00:17.000Z","msg":"一抄支那千萬黨員家<br />\n<br />\n美國財政儲備究竟可以多幾多兆美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能京都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:51:56.000Z","msg":"可能去到恒河沙添"},{"pid":"cc101390f9bbe8d1461b3323e2236a5c8b3b9821","tid":1709572,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64e68a4e212da358324a754b5dd458872015878","tid":1709572,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:23:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de5733b5834865f10069b75d8ad2c773e745618","tid":1709572,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T23:40:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}